        <div class="type-card-body"><h3>Reception &amp; studio signs</h3><p>Soft, premium halo glow that elevates any brand. Push through signs with acrylic faces and stainless steel returns for a refined, modern look.</p><div class="type-card-foot"><span class="type-card-link">Explore <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg></span></div></div>
